## Runtime Contract

- `state.json`: machine-readable runtime state
- `events.jsonl`: append-only supervisor and worker event stream
- `jobs/`: per-job metadata handoff files
- `notes/latest_summary.md`: latest human-readable checkpoint
- `outbox/`: rendered worker replies and pending reporting payloads

## Operator Notes

- The supervisor wakes Codex repeatedly instead of relying on one long session.
- The worker should prefer short, resumable bursts and keep state on disk.
